    "For example, γ risk increases during 2008 to account for the high uncertainty in the market during this period.",
    "Similarly, γ turn decreases during the same period, likely to allow us to trade more freely to satisfy the other constraints; interestingly γ trade increases during the same period, likely to push us toward more liquid stocks when trading increases.",
